*:

1. *Kasno* je bilo da se pokrene aktivnost. (It was too late to start the activity.) 
2. Svi su već otišli, pa smo *kasno* došli. (Everyone had already left, so we arrived late.)
3. *Kasnije* ću ti objasniti detalje. (I'll explain the details to you later.) 
4. *Kasnio* sam na sastanak. (I was late for the meeting.) 
5. Ona nikad ne dolazi *kasno*. (She never comes late.)